<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-1a' );" name="007-1a" class="pb">[007-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:209'>　禹貢長箋卷七　　　　　吳江朱鶴齡撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='209:216'>荆河惟豫州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='216:247'>　爾雅河南曰豫州<span class='krp-note'>郭璞註自/南河至漢</span>孔𫝊西南至荆山北距</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='247:280'>　河水<span class='krp-note'>荆山即南條荆山/河即冀州之南河</span>豫之河患次于兖故二州疆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='280:307'>　域並繫以河　朱子曰周公以土圭測天地之中<span class='krp-note'>今/登</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='307:335'>　<span class='krp-note'>封有測/景臺</span>則豫州為中至于北逺而南近此地形有偏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='335:358'>　耳所謂地不滿東南也　熊氏禾曰豫州當天下之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='358:384'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-1b' );" name="007-1b" class="pb">[007-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='384:407'>　中四方道里適均故古人于此定都不但形勢所在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='407:435'>　亦以朝㑹貢賦之便湯之亳今河南偃師是也<span class='krp-note'>按殷/有三</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='435:481'>　<span class='krp-note'>亳榖亳為南亳今歸徳府考城縣蒙亳為北亳今歸/徳府商丘縣偃師則西亳湯所都盤庚自耿遷殷即</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='481:518'>　<span class='krp-note'>此/</span>周之洛邑今河南洛陽是也<span class='krp-note'>本成周郟鄏地謂之/王城考王封周桓公</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='518:546'>　<span class='krp-note'>于此為/西周</span>其地北距河南抵荆山東抵徐西抵雍梁今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='546:574'>　為河南府虢郟鄭汝陳蔡唐鄧汴宋等州之地<span class='krp-note'>晉地/理志</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='574:597'>　<span class='krp-note'>豫州西自華山東至于/淮北自濟南界荆山</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='597:624'>　班固配十二次自氐五度至尾九度為大火之次<span class='krp-note'>費/直</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='624:650'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-2a' );" name="007-2a" class="pb">[007-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='650:694'>　<span class='krp-note'>起氐十一度蔡邕起氐八度爾雅大火謂之大/辰注大火心也蒼龍宿在中最明故時候主焉</span>於辰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='694:732'>　在卯宋之分野<span class='krp-note'>左傳帝遷閼伯于商丘主辰故/辰為商星商主大火宋分星也</span>屬豫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='732:763'>　州自柳九度至張十六度為鶉火之次<span class='krp-note'>費直起柳五/度蔡邕起三</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='763:806'>　<span class='krp-note'>度爾雅咮謂之柳柳鶉火也注東方蒼龍南/方朱鳥柳為朱鳥之口故名咮鶉即朱鳥也</span>于辰在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='806:847'>　午周之分野<span class='krp-note'>國語武王伐紂嵗在鶉火/是鶉火為周分也嵗嵗星</span>屬三河<span class='krp-note'>河東/河南</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='847:895'>　<span class='krp-note'>河内為三河摇春秋緯文耀鈎外方熊耳以至泗水/陪尾豫州屬  星  天官書夜半建者衡衡殷中州</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='895:928'>　<span class='krp-note'>河濟之間正義衡/北斗衡也殷當也</span>晉天文志房心宋豫州潁川入房</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='928:951'>　一度汝南入房二度沛郡入房四度梁國入房五度</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='951:977'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-2b' );" name="007-2b" class="pb">[007-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='977:1000'>　淮陽入心一度魯國入心三度楚國入房四度柳七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1000:1024'>　星張周三輔𢎞農入柳一度河南入七星三度河東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1024:1060'>　入張一度河内入張九度<span class='krp-note'>唐天文志近代言星土者/或以州或以國虞夏秦漢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1060:1106'>　<span class='krp-note'>郡國廢置不同周之興也王畿千里及其衰也僅得/河南七縣今則天下一統而直以鶉火為周分則疆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1106:1152'>　<span class='krp-note'>域舛矣七國之初天下地形雌韓而雄魏魏地西距/髙陵盡河東河内北有漳鄴東分梁宋至于汝南韓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1152:1198'>　<span class='krp-note'>據全鄭之地南盡潁川南陽西達虢畧距函谷固宜/陽北連上地皆綿亙數州相錯如繡考雲漢山河之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1198:1244'>　<span class='krp-note'>象多者或至十餘宿其后魏徙大梁則西河合于東/井秦拔宜陽而上黨入于輿鬼方戰國未滅時星家</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1244:1290'>　<span class='krp-note'>之言屢有明效今則同在畿甸之中而或者猶據漢/書地理志推之是守甘石遺術而不知變通之數者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1290:1316'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-3a' );" name="007-3a" class="pb">[007-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1316:1323'>　<span class='krp-note'>也/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1323:1354'>　周禮職方氏河南曰豫州其山鎮曰華<span class='krp-note'>賈耽曰周禮/職方以菑時</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1354:1397'>　<span class='krp-note'>為幽州之浸以華山為荆河之鎮有乖禹貢/應從闕疑按華山在今華隂禹時宜入雍州</span>其澤藪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1397:1432'>　曰圃田其川滎洛其浸波溠<span class='krp-note'>音詐按春秋傳楚子除/道梁溠營軍臨隨則溠</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1432:1466'>　<span class='krp-note'>宜入荆州今溠水在/徳安府隨州城東南</span>詩譜周東都王城畿内方六百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1466:1507'>　里<span class='krp-note'>王城即洛邑班固曰洛邑與宗周通封/畿東西長而南北短短長相覆為千里</span>其封域在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1507:1536'>　禹貢豫州太華外方之間北得河陽<span class='krp-note'>今懷慶/府孟縣</span>有冀州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1536:1559'>　之南通典豫州周宋魏韓其分野兼得秦楚之交秦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1559:1585'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-3b' );" name="007-3b" class="pb">[007-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1585:1608'>　置郡為三川碭潁川南陽郡之東北境南郡之北境</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1608:1631'>　漢武置十三州此為荆河州漢地理志周地今河南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1631:1654'>　之洛陽榖城平隂偃師鞏緱氏是其分周封微子于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1654:1681'>　宋今睢陽<span class='krp-note'>屬梁/國</span>本陶唐氏火正閼伯之墟宋後為齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1681:1709'>　楚魏三分魏得其梁陳留魏地自髙陵<span class='krp-note'>屬左/馮翊</span>以東盡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1709:1732'>　河東河内南有陳留及汝南之召陵㶏疆新汲西華</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1732:1759'>　長平潁川之舞陽郾許傿<span class='krp-note'>即/鄢</span>陵河南之開封中牟陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1759:1782'>　武酸棗卷皆魏分韓分晉得南陽郡及潁川之父城</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1782:1808'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-4a' );" name="007-4a" class="pb">[007-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1808:1832'>　定陵襄城潁陽潁隂長社陽翟郟東接汝南西接𢎞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1832:1869'>　農得新安宜陽皆韓分<span class='krp-note'>韓武子食采韓原分晉後都/平陽及滅鄭遂徙都焉即漢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1869:1896'>　<span class='krp-note'>新/鄭</span>詩風陳鄭之國與韓同星分鄭國今河南之新鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1896:1919'>　本髙辛氏火正祝融之墟及成臯滎陽潁川之崈髙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1919:1952'>　陽城皆鄭分右洛左泲食溱洧焉<span class='krp-note'>周宣王初封母弟/友于圻内咸林之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1952:1991'>　<span class='krp-note'>地今西安府華州子武公滅虢鄶居/之名之曰新鄭今開封府鄭州是</span>陳國今淮陽地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1991:2023'>　本太昊之墟潁川南陽則夏禹之國<span class='krp-note'>帝王世紀禹受/封為夏伯在豫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='2023:2059'>　<span class='krp-note'>州外方之南今/河南陽翟是</span>宛<span class='krp-note'>屬南/陽郡</span>西通武關東受江淮亦一都</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='2059:2085'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-4b' );" name="007-4b" class="pb">[007-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2085:2113'>　㑹也後漢郡國志豫州刺史<span class='krp-note'>治譙今/亳州</span>部郡國六潁川</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2113:2157'>　汝南<span class='krp-note'>分梁/沛立</span>梁國<span class='krp-note'>故秦/碭郡</span>沛國<span class='krp-note'>故秦泗/水郡</span>陳國<span class='krp-note'>本淮陽郡/明帝改</span>魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2157:2191'>　國<span class='krp-note'>故秦薛郡本屬徐/州光武改屬豫州</span>而𢎞農河南二郡為司隷校尉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2191:2219'>　部<span class='krp-note'>司隷治/河南</span>通考漢時為郡國八郡曰潁川河南陳留</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2219:2251'>　汝南沛南陽國曰梁淮陽又為漢中<span class='krp-note'>北境/是</span>𢎞農<span class='krp-note'>東境/是</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2251:2274'>　郡唐地理志河南道古豫州域洛陜負河而北為實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2274:2297'>　沈分負河而南虢汝許及新鄭之地為鶉火分鄭汴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2297:2320'>　陳蔡潁為壽星分宋亳為大火分通典唐分置十五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2320:2346'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-5a' );" name="007-5a" class="pb">[007-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2346:2390'>　部此為都畿<span class='krp-note'>採訪使/治東京</span>河南府<span class='krp-note'>洛/州</span>陜郡<span class='krp-note'>陜州本/𢎞農郡</span>臨汝<span class='krp-note'>汝/州</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2390:2435'>　滎陽<span class='krp-note'>鄭/州</span>郡<span class='krp-note'>並屬/都畿</span>河南道<span class='krp-note'>採訪使/治陳留</span>為陳留<span class='krp-note'>汴州折鄭/滑二州置</span>睢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2435:2483'>　陽<span class='krp-note'>宋/州</span>濟隂<span class='krp-note'>曹/州</span>譙郡<span class='krp-note'>亳/州</span>潁川<span class='krp-note'>許/州</span>淮陽<span class='krp-note'>陳/州</span>汝隂<span class='krp-note'>潁州本/信州</span>汝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2483:2524'>　南<span class='krp-note'>蔡州本/豫州</span>郡<span class='krp-note'>函史虢屬河南道初學記/襄州禹貢荆豫二州之界</span>宋史開封府</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2524:2555'>　屬京畿路應天興仁<span class='krp-note'>本曹/州</span>二府拱州廣濟軍<span class='krp-note'>漢定/陶</span>屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2555:2578'>　京東西路襄陽府鄧隨金均唐五州光化軍屬京西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2578:2619'>　南路<span class='krp-note'>内金州南渡/後隷利州路</span>河南潁昌<span class='krp-note'>今開封/府許州</span>淮寧<span class='krp-note'>今陳/州</span>順昌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2619:2648'>　<span class='krp-note'>今鳯陽/府潁州</span>四府鄭孟蔡汝四州信陽軍屬京西北路亳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2648:2674'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-5b' );" name="007-5b" class="pb">[007-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2674:2715'>　州屬淮南東路<span class='krp-note'>通考以單州屬豫考單州地為單父/碭山魚臺城武應屬徐州  宋京東</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2715:2761'>　<span class='krp-note'>路得兖豫青徐之域西抵大梁南極淮泗東北至海/京西路得冀豫荆兖梁五州之域而豫州為多東暨</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2761:2794'>　<span class='krp-note'>汝潁西被陜服南/畧鄢郢北扺河津</span>大明一統志古豫州為今河南省</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2794:2838'>　歸徳<span class='krp-note'>春秋宋地秦置碭郡漢為梁國隋置宋州唐置/宣武軍節度宋為南京應天府其地廣衍面淮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2838:2885'>　<span class='krp-note'>負/河</span>河南<span class='krp-note'>周東都秦置三川郡漢置河南郡東漢改河/南尹三國魏置司州北魏自代徙都之北周</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2885:2931'>　<span class='krp-note'>及隋唐皆為東都宋為西京金號中京/其地左成臯右澠池前伊闕後大河</span>南陽<span class='krp-note'>周申鄧/二國地</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2931:2977'>　<span class='krp-note'>春秋屬楚戰國屬韓秦自漢江以北置南陽郡漢屬/荆州晉為南陽國及順陽義陽二郡境西魏為重鎮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2977:3024'>　<span class='krp-note'>唐曰鄧州宋曰宛州其地在洛/陽之南襄陽之北膏沃稱陸海</span>汝寧<span class='krp-note'>春秋沈蔡二國/戰國楚魏之境</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='3024:3050'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-6a' );" name="007-6a" class="pb">[007-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='3050:3096'>　<span class='krp-note'>秦屬潁川漢置汝南郡劉宋為重鎮號懸瓠城東魏/置豫州治此唐曰蔡州宋置淮康軍其地襟帶長淮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='3096:3139'>　<span class='krp-note'>控扼潁蔡/四方最中</span>四府其開封府<span class='krp-note'>春秋鄭衞陳杞地秦屬三/川漢置陳留郡隋唐曰汴</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='3139:3185'>　<span class='krp-note'>州興元初徙宣武節度使治此五代梁都之號東京/晉漢周及宋因焉金號南京元曰汴梁其地南與楚</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='3185:3227'>　<span class='krp-note'>境西與韓境北與/趙境東與齊境</span>則兖豫二州域<span class='krp-note'>祥符陳留杞縣通/許太康尉氏洧川</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='3227:3269'>　<span class='krp-note'>鄢陵扶溝中牟蘭陽儀封及/陳許禹鄭四州所屬屬豫州</span>湖廣襄陽府<span class='krp-note'>詳見/荆州</span>則荆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='3269:3311'>　豫二州域<span class='krp-note'>襄陽棗陽榖城光化均州屬豫州考襄陽/府誌又以榖城屬荆宜城屬豫鄭端簡云</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='3311:3332'>　<span class='krp-note'>山東曹州西南地及/定陶縣當屬豫州</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='3332:3355'>　范仲淹曰洛陽險固表裏山河接應東京連屬關陜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='3355:3381'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-6b' );" name="007-6b" class="pb">[007-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='3381:3404'>　而汴為四戰之地太平宜居汴有事必居洛陽章俊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='3404:3427'>　卿曰酈食其荀文若之徒皆稱陳留為天下之衝四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='3427:3450'>　通五達之郊秦漢迄南北朝天下有變嘗為戰場王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='3450:3473'>　伯之興未有都于汴者自隋煬帝大開汴河直達淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='3473:3497'>　泗而大梁實坐要㑹振南北水陸之衡形𫝑百倍李</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3497:3520'>　唐屹為重鎮宋仍五代之舊都之大抵長安以陜西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3520:3543'>　為畿輔而屏蔽實在隴右洛陽以關東為畿輔而屏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3543:3566'>　蔽實在河東大梁以河南為畿輔而屏蔽實在河北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3566:3592'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-7a' );" name="007-7a" class="pb">[007-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3592:3615'>　　丘濬曰三代以前洛為中國之中以今天下觀之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='3615:3638'>　則南北袤而東西蹙其所謂中蓋在荆襄之間　愚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='3638:3666'>　按今之河南實兼河北<span class='krp-note'>懷衞彰/三府</span>春秋天王狩河陽又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3666:3689'>　以陽樊温原攅茅之田與晉考之皆周畿内地則周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3689:3712'>　時豫州已跨河北而有之蓋河陽當河東之要㑹為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3712:3735'>　西洛北門洛邑周東都故隷在内服以廣外屏其後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3735:3758'>　河内畀晉文而周地益狹至秦併六國必先亡周者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3758:3781'>　六國叩關以洛陽為孔道周滅則横據鞏洛東出伊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3781:3807'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-7b' );" name="007-7b" class="pb">[007-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3807:3830'>　闕而韓魏震南通陳許而荆楚摇扼天下之腹心斷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3830:3853'>　諸侯之從約而趙代燕齊以次舉矣楚漢相拒亦多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='3853:3877'>　于成臯廣武滎陽京索間蓋漢據關中其𫝑即秦之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='3877:3900'>　勢而楚割鴻溝以西為漢則山河之險盡去其亡豈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='3900:3923'>　待垓下哉又按宋都大梁本非太祖意鄭漁仲謂無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='3923:3946'>　設險之山則國失憑依無流惡之水則民多疾癘是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='3946:3969'>　也宋不得幽薊故河北亦不可都然商都河北屢有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='3969:3992'>　河患三國五胡之時都鄴都邢臺者亦未見其長乆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='3992:4018'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-8a' );" name="007-8a" class="pb">[007-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='4018:4041'>　也使太祖不狥晉王之請遂都洛陽國勢豈至於積</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='4041:4064'>　弱哉李綱謂鄧州古南陽西隣關陜可以召兵北近</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4064:4087'>　京畿可以遣援南通巴蜀可取貨財東達江淮可運</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='4087:4110'>　穀粟若以定都建康不及此蓋就紹興初時事而論</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='4110:4133'>　耳　魏校曰中絡岷山為祖自蜀入隴結於初龍則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='4133:4156'>　為長安結于中龍則為洛陽南絡傳大江放於海北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='4156:4179'>　絡傳大河放于海惟中絡止于嵩髙其前平夷凡幾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='4179:4202'>　千里而泰山特起東方張左右翼為障以天下大勢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='4202:4228'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-8b' );" name="007-8b" class="pb">[007-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='4228:4251'>　言之長安龍首穴也洛陽龍心穴也兹其大龍之腹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='4251:4275'>　乎宋都大梁亦在龍腹而國勢弱者汴坦無備其𫝑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='4275:4298'>　必宿重兵民力坐而困矣予嘗至洛陽相其形勢熊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='4298:4322'>　耳祖龍𤼵自終南逺則太行為後托近則嵩髙為左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='4322:4345'>　障然終南自為長安前朝太行亦為平陽左障嵩髙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='4345:4368'>　雖為障洛陽而大情自欲東出與萬里平原作祖然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='4368:4391'>　後黙識天道之公大地相為勾連其融結非一處王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='4391:4411'>　氣𤼵乆而歇又轉之他宇宙所以無窮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='4411:4437'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-9a' );" name="007-9a" class="pb">[007-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='4437:4455'>伊洛瀍澗既入于河<span class='krp-note'>洛漢書/作雒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='4455:4488'>　漢地理志伊水出𢎞農郡盧氏縣<span class='krp-note'>今河南府陜州盧/氏縣古西虢地</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='4488:4527'>　東熊耳山<span class='krp-note'>括地志熊耳山在虢/州盧氏縣南五十里</span>東北入洛過郡一<span class='krp-note'>𢎞/農</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='4527:4550'>　行四百五十里水經注東北至洛陽縣南北入于洛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='4550:4573'>　愚按山海經水經謂伊源出南陽縣西蔓渠山孔傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='4573:4602'>　謂出陸渾山<span class='krp-note'>在今河南/府嵩縣</span>淮南子謂出上魏山俱與地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='4602:4631'>　理志不合自郭璞注熊耳在上洛縣<span class='krp-note'>今西安/府商州</span>南而蔡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='4631:4654'>　傳因之考一統志伊水源出盧氏悶頓嶺導山熊耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='4654:4680'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-9b' );" name="007-9b" class="pb">[007-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='4680:4703'>　亦在豫州界則漢志固得其真矣漢地理志洛水出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='4703:4733'>　𢎞農郡上洛縣冢嶺山東北至河南郡鞏縣<span class='krp-note'>今河南/府鞏縣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='4733:4771'>　<span class='krp-note'>周惠公封少子/于此為東周君</span>入河過郡二<span class='krp-note'>𢎞農/河南</span>行千七十里水經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='4771:4808'>　出京兆上洛縣讙舉山<span class='krp-note'>山海經讙舉之山洛水出焉/蔡傳冢嶺山水經謂之讙舉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='4808:4845'>　<span class='krp-note'>山/</span>東北過鞏縣東又北入于河<span class='krp-note'>山海經洛水成臯西/入河一統志洛水經</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='4845:4890'>　<span class='krp-note'>盧氏永寧宜陽洛陽偃師鞏縣入于河河南通志/洛河在河南府城南三里至鞏縣北十里入黄河</span>漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='4890:4924'>　地理志瀍水出河南郡榖城縣<span class='krp-note'>故城在今洛/陽縣西北</span>㬱<span class='krp-note'>音/潛</span>亭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='4924:4947'>　北東南入洛水經注榖城北有㬱亭瀍水出其北梓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='4947:4974'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-10a' );" name="007-10a" class="pb">[007-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='4974:5015'>　澤中<span class='krp-note'>一統志榖城山舊名㬱亭山在河南府/城西北五十里連孟津縣界瀍水所出</span>東過偃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='5015:5039'>　師縣又東入于洛漢地理志澗水出𢎞農郡新安縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='5039:5063'>　東南入洛水經出新安縣南白石山蔡傳古新安在今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='5063:5090'>　河南府新安澠<span class='krp-note'>音/勉</span>池之間今澠池縣東二十三里新</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='5090:5125'>　安城是也<span class='krp-note'>括地志新安故城在今洛/州澠池縣東一十三里</span>城東北有白石</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='5125:5148'>　山即澗水所出酈道元云世謂之廣陽山然則澗水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='5148:5183'>　出今之澠池至新安入洛也<span class='krp-note'>河南通志澗水源有二/一出澠池縣白石山一</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='5183:5216'>　<span class='krp-note'>出盧氏縣香爐山俱/流至洛陽縣入洛</span>王樵曰豫之洛猶雍之渭而書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='5216:5243'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-10b' );" name="007-10b" class="pb">[007-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='5243:5266'>　法不同涇灃漆沮雖皆入渭而水之大小不同故曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='5266:5289'>　屬曰從曰同各别志之伊洛瀍澗四水相敵故統志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='5289:5327'>　其入河與江漢同文<span class='krp-note'>曹學佺曰三川河洛伊也其形/若鼎李格非曰伊洛二水分注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='5327:5357'>　<span class='krp-note'>河南城中伊/水尤清澈</span>　茅瑞徵曰豫州雖北距河已自兖入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='5357:5380'>　海此外水惟伊洛瀍澗而洛為最大故禹治豫水先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='5380:5402'>　於此自此而東則滎波自此而又東則菏澤孟豬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='5402:5425'>　王綱振曰濟洛二水同在豫州入河濟大而洛小乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='5425:5448'>　洛為一州之専患濟則數州之公患其雷夏澤大野</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='5448:5475'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-11a' );" name="007-11a" class="pb">[007-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='5475:5499'>　　豬濟水之治已散見兖徐諸州惟洛出入皆在豫所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='5499:5524'>　　以與雍州之渭同一𤼵例以經四州之河濟終後於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='5524:5549'>　　一州之洛亦賔主之辨也　魏校曰長安洛陽大𤼵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='5549:5573'>　　于周而其機啟自神禹龍門鑿而涇灃漆沮㑹於渭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='5573:5597'>　　汭入河長安始可都矣伊闕鑿而伊與瀍澗㑹于洛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='5597:5610'>　　汭入河洛陽始可都矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='5610:5616'>滎波既豬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='5616:5639'>　蔡傳濟水潛行絶河南溢為滎在今鄭州滎澤縣西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='5639:5666'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-11b' );" name="007-11b" class="pb">[007-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='5666:5700'>　五里古敖倉<span class='krp-note'>今開封府河隂縣敖山/秦時敖氏築倉于上</span>東南水經注濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='5700:5731'>　水又東逕滎澤北故滎水所都也<span class='krp-note'>述征記滎澤在/中牟西東西四</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='5731:5777'>　<span class='krp-note'>十里許南北二百里許京相璠曰滎澤在滎陽縣東/南按今開封府鄭州有滎陽滎澤二縣古滎水在滎</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='5777:5806'>　<span class='krp-note'>澤縣西/北五里</span>即隂溝之上源自西漢末濟水不復南溢滎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='5806:5830'>　澤口受河水有石門謂之滎口石門地形殊卑鄭𤣥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='5830:5853'>　云滎今塞為平地滎陽民猶名其處為滎澤在其縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='5853:5899'>　東<span class='krp-note'>正義春秋閔二年衞狄戰于滎澤鄭𤣥云即此杜/預云此滎澤當在河北以衞敗方始渡戰處必在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='5899:5931'>　<span class='krp-note'>河北疑此澤跨河/南北而得名也</span>爾雅水自洛出為波山海經婁涿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='5931:5958'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-12a' );" name="007-12a" class="pb">[007-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='5958:5990'>　之山波水出于其隂北流注于榖水<span class='krp-note'>洛陽記榖水在/洛陽城西三十</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='5990:6022'>　<span class='krp-note'>里郭璞曰波水/世謂之百答水</span>水經注洛水自上洛縣東北出為門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='6022:6046'>　水北逕𢎞農縣故城東注于河即爾雅所謂洛出為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='6046:6091'>　波<span class='krp-note'>按水經注又引應劭說波水出孤山南入滍水馬/端臨云孤山即今歇馬嶺在臨汝郡魯山縣西北</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='6091:6122'>　<span class='krp-note'>此與禹貢波/水名同實别</span>愚按波溠見周禮當以爾雅為據傳疏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='6122:6145'>　謂滎之波水已豬馬鄭王本波作播謂此澤名滎播</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='6145:6174'>　俱謬　酈道元謂禹塞淫水于滎陽下<span class='krp-note'>濟為河/所淫</span>引河東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='6174:6197'>　南以通淮泗濟水分河東南流漢志所云滎陽縣有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='6197:6224'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-12b' );" name="007-12b" class="pb">[007-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='6224:6247'>　蒗蕩渠首受濟者是也漢明帝時河流既塞議築汴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='6247:6275'>　渠使樂浪人王景作堤<span class='krp-note'>今名/金堤</span>起自滎陽東至千乘海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='6275:6298'>　口千有餘里十里一水門更相洄注渠流東至浚儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='6298:6336'>　<span class='krp-note'>今祥/符縣</span>名浚儀渠<span class='krp-note'>蔡傳南曰蒗蕩北/曰浚儀其實一也</span>其後靈帝時於敖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='6336:6359'>　城西北累石為門以遏渠口又名石門渠石門渠東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='6359:6382'>　合濟水與河渠東注至敖山北而受汴水汴水又東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='6382:6413'>　至滎陽北自廣武二城<span class='krp-note'>即楚漢戰處/在今河隂縣</span>間東流而出濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='6413:6446'>　水至此乃絶隋大業初<span class='krp-note'>煬/帝</span>𤼵丁夫百萬自板渚<span class='krp-note'>在虎/牢東</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='6446:6473'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-13a' );" name="007-13a" class="pb">[007-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='6473:6496'>　引河歴滎澤入汴又自大梁之東引汴水入泗達淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='6496:6532'>　千有餘里更名通濟渠<span class='krp-note'>元和郡縣志汴渠在河隂縣/南即蒗蕩渠隋名通濟渠</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='6532:6555'>　唐宋轉漕因之　張洎曰禹于滎澤下分大河為隂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='6555:6578'>　溝引注東南至大梁浚儀縣西北復分二渠一渠東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='6578:6606'>　經陽武縣<span class='krp-note'>今屬開/封府</span>中牟臺下為官渡一渠始皇疏鑿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='6606:6629'>　以灌魏都為鴻溝蒗蕩渠自滎陽五池口東來注之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='6629:6652'>　其鴻溝即出河之溝亦曰蒗蕩渠愚按滎澤之口與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='6652:6686'>　汴河口通其水深可以灌大梁<span class='krp-note'>陳亮曰禹于滎澤下/引河南注其流猶未</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='6686:6713'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-13b' );" name="007-13b" class="pb">[007-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='6713:6759'>　<span class='krp-note'>盛自秦王賁決浚儀灌魏而河汴始分流漢承秦受/河患尤劇續述征記汴河到浚儀而分汴東注河南</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='6759:6785'>　<span class='krp-note'>流/</span>即鴻溝也戰國䇿蘇秦說魏曰大王之地南有鴻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='6785:6808'>　溝則鴻溝自蘇秦時已有之張洎謂始皇所鑿似誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='6808:6831'>　　黄度曰水經注禹塞滎水於滎陽下引河通淮泗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='6831:6854'>　名蒗蕩渠一名浚儀渠一名通濟渠一名汴渠然則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='6854:6877'>　河西道通淮矣濟逾河為滎菏被孟通泗皆有名見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='6877:6900'>　源流相屬汴于經無名見非禹瀆也禹濬畎澮距川</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='6900:6923'>　川皆大瀆行于兩山之間澮洫則皆人為之也徐豫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='6923:6950'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-14a' );" name="007-14a" class="pb">[007-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='6950:6973'>　地平井畫端整凡今隂溝汳睢諸水皆無原本皆溝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='6973:6996'>　澮井絡互相灌輸皆當受水于菏濟者也自蒗蕩通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='6996:7019'>　河滎澤既廢故皆受水于蒗蕩耳蒗蕩出河斷非禹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='7019:7042'>　跡禹治行河本以河湍悍難行平地故釃二渠以引</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='7042:7065'>　河而後載之髙地二渠非得已也後世不識聖人之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='7065:7089'>　意妄鑿河為瀆或不順地阞水屬不理孫故其𫝑易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='7089:7112'>　決蓋非獨蒗蕩也其後濮水通河而酸棗決瓠水通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='7112:7135'>　河而瓠子決汴渠亦屢決至王景治汴鑿山開澗十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='7135:7162'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-14b' );" name="007-14b" class="pb">[007-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='7162:7185'>　里置門使水更相回注紊亂渠脈而禹跡益壞矣且</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='7185:7208'>　所為通淮泗者以舟楫之利也菏已通矣而何更用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='7208:7231'>　通蒗蕩哉其曰禹塞淫水而鑿之者春秋戰國䇿謀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='7231:7265'>　之士托其名於禹而世不察也<span class='krp-note'>陳無已汳水新渠記/云禹時河南無濟世</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='7265:7306'>　<span class='krp-note'>謂蒗蕩受濟禹塞滎陽而用河者皆失之/是黄説所祖與蘇子瞻不合然極有理</span>　唐開元</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='7306:7329'>　中江南租船自淮西北泝鴻溝轉輸河隂含嘉太原</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='7329:7352'>　等倉凡三年運米七百萬石宋都汴嵗漕六百萬石</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='7352:7375'>　東南自淮入汴至京師陜西自三門白波轉黄河入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='7375:7402'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-15a' );" name="007-15a" class="pb">[007-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='7402:7429'>　汴至京師陳蔡自惠民河<span class='krp-note'>即閔/河</span>至京師京東自廣濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='7429:7452'>　河至京師凡四路皆汴河是賴其時近都城者惟汴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='7452:7475'>　蔡諸水而黄河經城之東北以達于海至元時河始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='7475:7498'>　南徙逼城流合汴泗入淮明代正統時嘗分決張秋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='7498:7521'>　口東北入海後復東南入海如故夫治河之法或疏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='7521:7544'>　或塞無容執一然治河于滎澤之間則宜疏濬多而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='7544:7574'>　隄防少蓋滎澤孫家渡口至項城南頓<span class='krp-note'>開封項城縣/有南頓城</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='7574:7597'>　二百里間涓流時淤河身淺隘水無所容故其湍悍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='7597:7624'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-15b' );" name="007-15b" class="pb">[007-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='7624:7649'>　之𫝑不可遽回惟疏濬深廣使水𫝑少殺則決口可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='7649:7662'>　塞矣<span class='krp-note'>輯考索/諸書</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='7662:7688'>導菏澤被孟豬<span class='krp-note'>菏音柯孟豬漢書作/盟豬史記作明都</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='7688:7722'>　孔傳菏澤在胡陵<span class='krp-note'>漢志胡陵縣屬山陽郡/故城在今魚臺縣東</span>水經南濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='7722:7761'>　東過寃句<span class='krp-note'>音淵/劬</span>縣<span class='krp-note'>故城在/今曹州</span>南又東過定陶縣<span class='krp-note'>今兖州/府曹州</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='7761:7788'>　<span class='krp-note'>定陶/縣</span>南又東北菏水出焉又云濟水東流者過乘氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='7788:7831'>　縣<span class='krp-note'>注見/徐州</span>又東過昌邑<span class='krp-note'>今兖州府/金鄉縣</span>東緡<span class='krp-note'>今併入/金鄉</span>方與<span class='krp-note'>今/兖</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='7831:7859'>　<span class='krp-note'>州府魚/臺縣</span>縣北為菏水菏水又東過胡陵縣南東入泗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='7859:7886'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-16a' );" name="007-16a" class="pb">[007-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='7886:7931'>　水<span class='krp-note'>酈注菏水與泗水㑹于胡陵縣西六十里俗謂之/黄水口黄水西北通鉅野澤沼注于菏故因以名</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='7931:7957'>　<span class='krp-note'>焉/</span>至下邳入淮括地志菏澤在曹州濟隂縣東北九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='7957:7989'>　十里定陶縣東今名龍池<span class='krp-note'>一統志菏澤在/曹州境内今涸</span>漢地理志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='7989:8028'>　盟諸<span class='krp-note'>即孟豬左傳爾雅俱作孟/諸周禮作望諸屬青州</span>澤在梁國睢陽縣<span class='krp-note'>今/歸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='8028:8063'>　<span class='krp-note'>徳府商/丘縣</span>東北蔡傳今應天府虞城縣<span class='krp-note'>即今歸徳/府虞城縣</span>西北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='8063:8086'>　孟諸澤是也左傳楚子夢河神曰賜汝孟諸之麋即</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='8086:8109'>　此正義地理志謂山陽郡有胡陵縣不言其縣有菏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='8109:8132'>　澤也又謂菏澤在濟隂定陶縣東孟豬在梁國睢陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='8132:8159'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-16b' );" name="007-16b" class="pb">[007-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='8159:8182'>　縣東北以今地騐之則胡陵在睢陽之東定陶在睢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='8182:8205'>　陽之北其水皆不流溢被孟豬然郡縣之名隨代變</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='8205:8228'>　易古之胡陵當在睢陽之西北故得東出被孟豬也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='8228:8251'>　闞駰曰不言入而言被者明不常入也水盛乃覆被</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='8251:8274'>　之王樵曰孟豬之藪可田則有水草而淺涸時多故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='8274:8297'>　導菏水之溢時乎被孟豬也澤無言導者此二澤相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='8297:8320'>　通故可以導此及彼　黄度曰導菏澤被孟豬蓋因</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='8320:8344'>　窪下之𫝑導而行之淺流覆被非若後人之斸鑿為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='8344:8371'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-17a' );" name="007-17a" class="pb">[007-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='8371:8394'>　深渠也　金氏履祥曰自菏澤至孟豬凡百四十里</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='8394:8417'>　二水舊相通今菏澤自分南北清河近時大河亦被</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='8417:8456'>　孟豬併行睢水矣<span class='krp-note'>考宋京東漕渠起青淄歴齊鄆涉/梁山濼入五丈渠達汴五丈渠即</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='8456:8483'>　<span class='krp-note'>菏澤/也</span>愚按玉海云今東平濟南淄川北海界中有水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='8483:8506'>　流入于海謂之清河實菏澤山東通志亦以菏澤為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='8506:8529'>　濟水所㑹入海水經則云合泗入淮蓋自漢武時河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='8529:8552'>　注鉅野通淮泗而濟流亦從之南溢合泗入淮者漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='8552:8574'>　以後之濟桑欽所名南濟也入海當是禹時故蹟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='8574:8601'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-17b' );" name="007-17b" class="pb">[007-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='8601:8624'>　茅瑞徵曰滎與菏澤皆以志濟也滎波在豫西北菏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='8624:8647'>　孟在豫東北澤與豬不同豬是蓄而復流澤是水之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='8647:8651'>　聚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='8651:8661'>厥土惟壤下土墳壚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='8661:8685'>　蔡傳土不言色者其色雜也顔氏曰𤣥而疏者謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='8685:8720'>　壚<span class='krp-note'>釋名土黑曰壚壚然解/散也説文壚黑剛土也</span>其土有髙下之不同故别</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='8720:8743'>　言之吕覽凡耕之道必始于壚為其寡澤而後枯王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='8743:8766'>　氏炎曰壤則沃墳壚則為瘠王樵曰周禮草人掌土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='8766:8793'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-18a' );" name="007-18a" class="pb">[007-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='8793:8821'>　化之法凡糞種墳壤用麋渇澤用鹿<span class='krp-note'>渴水/涸也</span>博物志麋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='8821:8844'>　聚草澤而食其場成泥名曰麋暖民隨之種稻其收</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='8844:8868'>　百倍此即今人糞田法草人土化之法恐亦是𩔖也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='8868:8891'>　墳壤潤解也渴澤故水處即經所云墳壚也　袁黄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='8891:8914'>　曰他州辨土性只一言之青之海濵豫之下土特别</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='8914:8937'>　而志之者以如是之土頗多也財賦所生聖人謹焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='8937:8949'>厥田惟中上厥賦錯上中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='8949:8972'>　田第四賦第二又雜出第一茅瑞徵曰雜出之等髙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='8972:8999'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-18b' );" name="007-18b" class="pb">[007-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='8999:9022'>　于正額故先言錯邵寶曰賦錯出者他州無與焉升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='9022:9048'>　降之説非是<span class='krp-note'>臨川吳氏謂豫賦與/冀相乗除為上下</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='9048:9071'>　愚按今南陽汝寧之地直走襄黄地多蕪曠宋太宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='9071:9094'>　遷雲朔之民於汝鄭墾田頗廣厥後孟忠襄屯守其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='9094:9117'>　處稱重鎮焉丘文莊謂天下之田南方多水北方多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='9117:9140'>　陸荆襄唐鄧問兼水陸而有之南北流民僑寓者衆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='9140:9163'>　宜于兩藩交界中募南人耕水田北人耕陸田按畝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='9163:9186'>　分租隨地儲積或遇河洛關陜荒歉亦可用以救濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='9186:9213'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-19a' );" name="007-19a" class="pb">[007-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='9213:9234'>　嗟乎此議若行中原之地豈至為巨冦逋聚哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='9234:9250'>厥貢漆枲絺紵厥篚纎纊錫貢磬錯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='9250:9273'>　林氏之竒曰周官載師漆林之征二十有五周以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='9273:9296'>　征而此則貢者蓋豫州在周為畿内故載師掌其征</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='9296:9319'>　而不制貢禹時豫在畿外故有貢推此則知冀不言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='9319:9359'>　貢之意矣<span class='krp-note'>今漆出南陽府南召淅川葛出汝寧/府信陽州及光山固始見河南通志</span>説文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='9359:9386'>　紵檾<span class='krp-note'>音/頃</span>屬陸璣云亦麻也陳詩東門之池可以漚紵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='9386:9422'>　<span class='krp-note'>杜預曰呉地貴/縞鄭地貴紵</span>顔師古曰織紵以為布及練<span class='krp-note'>練熟素/繒也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='9422:9449'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-19b' );" name="007-19b" class="pb">[007-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='9449:9488'>　纖見徐州纊細綿也<span class='krp-note'>小爾雅絮之細者曰纊訓按孔/傳纖纊細綿也是以纖  細徐</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='9488:9528'>　<span class='krp-note'>州之纖亦訓細蔡傳纊細綿而于纖/字無訓蓋解同𤣥纖之纖當從之</span>正義磬有以玉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='9528:9558'>　為之者故傳云治玉石曰錯謂治磬錯也<span class='krp-note'>錯字從金/鑄鐵為之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='9558:9585'>　<span class='krp-note'>今鑢/是</span>呉氏泳曰龜非貢物故言納不言貢橘柚磬錯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='9585:9608'>　雖是貢物非常制為貢也故言錫貢蔡傳揚州先言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='9608:9631'>　橘柚此先言錫貢者橘柚言包于厥篚之文無嫌故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='9631:9654'>　言錫貢在後磬錯則嫌與厥篚之文相屬故言錫貢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='9654:9677'>　在先　茅瑞徵曰豫州職貢畧與兖似蓋二州皆近</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='9677:9704'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-20a' );" name="007-20a" class="pb">[007-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='9704:9727'>　冀冀甸服専貢粟米二州近京師則専供服御禹制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='9727:9743'>　貢先服食器用次之珍幣又次之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='9743:9751'>浮于洛達于河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='9751:9774'>　蔡傳豫州去帝都最近東境徑自入河西境則浮洛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='9774:9797'>　而後至也　丘濬曰堯都平陽商都亳成王營洛邑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='9797:9820'>　皆以河為運道後世都汴洛者皆由汴水入河都長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='9820:9844'>　安者雖不瀕河亦必由河入渭是古今建都無有不資</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='9844:9867'>　于河道者一統志汴河舊在滎陽縣東經開封府城</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='9867:9894'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '007-20b' );" name="007-20b" class="pb">[007-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='9894:9934'>　内又東合蔡河<span class='krp-note'>蔡河本名琵琶溝在浚儀是秦漢故/運道隋開汴河不復由此唐杜佑復</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='9934:9972'>　<span class='krp-note'>濬之尉宋史蔡河貫京師閔/水自  氏入焉是為惠民河</span>名蒗蕩渠東注泗州下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='9972:9995'>　入于淮近因河决蔡河湮没無跡而汴河自府西中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='9995:10004'>　牟縣入黄河矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='10004:10007'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='10007:10010'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='10010:10013'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='10013:10022'>　禹貢長箋卷七</span><br/>
